WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.700 --> 00:00:06.040
Cheeks with red wine, a dish rich in stewed meat.

00:00:07.340 --> 00:00:21.500
INGREDIENTS 4 People

1.3kg of Cheeks
1 Large Onion
2 cloves of garlic
4 Carrots
4 Medium Potatoes
1 bay leaf
2 Glasses of Red Wine
Water
Black pepper
Olive oil
Salt

00:00:23.780 --> 00:00:53.840
1. We cut the vegetables finely
2. In a casserole with a little olive oil, we poach the vegetables.

00:01:05.780 --> 00:01:13.940
3. When we have the poached vegetables, we add the red wine.

00:01:16.180 --> 00:01:27.400
4. We clean and chop the cheeks.

00:01:34.060 --> 00:01:47.300
5. Season the cheeks with salt and black pepper.
6. Chop the cheek slightly with the vegetables and add the other glass of red wine.

00:01:48.520 --> 00:01:56.220
7. Cover with water and let cook over medium heat 1 hour and 30 minutes.

00:01:59.240 --> 00:02:24.300
8. Cut the potatoes and fry them in plenty of olive oil.

00:02:27.900 --> 00:02:33.140
Put the cheeks on a plate and accompany them with the chips.

Remember Robarecetillas that cooking can be fun, Goodbye !!!

